title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update II - New York City - photogrammetry off  vs photogrammetry on
description:
In this video we will look at the New York city which is part of World Update II: USA which has been released this week. In this video I want to show you the difference between photogrammetry off and on. This is based on the video published earlier this week for New York city where the photogrammetry mode was switched off.
